Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:35.01,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:43.02,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Number,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,1)\c&H16B8F0&}Flag {\c&H8000C8&}13
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:43.02,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,1)\fs26}If {\c&HA351E6&}His {\c&H45C887&}Flag {\c&HCCC35D&}Breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:50.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I'm going \Nto sing for Hatate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:52.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,my songs can give hope to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:09.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not able to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll dance and cheer you all on! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me, Souta-oniisama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on our manly friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:23.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,that I shall take care \Nof Souta-kun's enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:32.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-san said he needed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:34.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I need him, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,if that's okay with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:43.70,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.52,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You were out here by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.17,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and I wasn't able to be \Na big sister for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.57,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.39,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:56.26,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Your big sister will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:05.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,Any one who makes Souta boy cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:08.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,will be getting a spanking from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Older sisters aren't the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,who get to save onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I am not part of the Council of \Nthe Seven Virtues any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hatate Souta's Samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Daimyouzamurai Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the ones giving \NSouta a hard time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:33.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm from a parallel world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:34.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate-kun, I'm going \Nto save you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Bullying Souta is against school rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:53.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't repay you for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I... got something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,very special from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:09.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I was empty when I couldn't \Nsee that girl anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and I wanted to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You had me experience all \Nof those wonderful feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and that made me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,who I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nanami-chan and \Nthe rest feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:58.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't match them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,They're nothing more \Nthan virtual people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's absorbing its \Nallies and powering up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last boss flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Angel Boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun! Granny! Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee! Megumu! Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.03,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to make it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.04,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The main server's going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.61,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.93,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.19,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some sort of special
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.01,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,death flag I can use to defeat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.31,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.88,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There's a special death \Nflag I can use right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.41,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.90,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.05,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.13,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:35.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,behind the Premium \NAmbriel that I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.55,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where everything began...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.26,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to die here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.15,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:51.48,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I just got to be friends \Nwith all of you and Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.22,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Okiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.05,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.39,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll all be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,My brother is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.14,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.69,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If we reach the deck, I'm sure \Nthere'll be lifeboats available.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If we can just make it to one of those...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.79,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.67,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't start spacing out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.02,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.15,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.54,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, is something over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:20.77,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.49,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.25,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.61,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.93,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.19,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.33,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.69,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to try and save someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.11,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Save someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.49,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.58,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.60,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Laplace's Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.12,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.63,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.25,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.05,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.18,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.68,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lift that off of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.93,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.18,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.44,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.96,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:29.94,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.18,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.36,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.86,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.36,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.65,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.15,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.17,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.61,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:30.67,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:31.97,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.83,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.78,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Only natural to try and save someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.38,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.11,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to get some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.04,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.42,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So... So, I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.43,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this is the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:30.27,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like anyone will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.49,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.32,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayed by the person you saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.07,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.49,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.22,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,die here alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:55.97,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,I guess humans are the same, \Nno matter the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.87,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like there's anything \Nleft to see in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.30,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.51,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.85,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We'll get you out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,C,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're going to lift this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.32,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to save you, Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.82,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.06,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.65,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,One.. two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.83,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.90,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I doubt them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.14,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.56,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone going to die here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.61,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.75,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,their fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.70,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,What if I told you there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,way to change their fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:00.81,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:03.36,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate everyone will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.37,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,This is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:07.63,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.69,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,This is a death flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.07,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A death flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:14.66,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,A flag is a mechanism that \Ncauses a branch in fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:18.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.60,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.25,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.80,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,you have no death flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.21,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,You're also the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.18,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,who can alter everyone's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.94,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.98,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:40.16,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Collect everyone's death flags into one,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.33,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,and carry their fate for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.98,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.84,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's life is not equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:06.22,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,You shall be tormented \Nby every sort of despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.73,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,and reach closer and closer to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.35,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,That's the price to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.92,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Will everyone be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.53,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.64,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Give everyone's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.75,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,death flags to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.77,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.25,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:44.51,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,I will erase this event \Nfrom everyone's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,You will never have met them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.92,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,You will live in solitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.26,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,and hate yourself for the choice you made,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,hate the people who put you through a living hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:59.52,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,or perhaps hate the world itself for making you experience this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.13,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,and while cursing them all, \Nlive out your final days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.23,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't curse them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.28,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:14.12,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I know the hearts of everyone \Nin this world are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:17.34,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why no matter how \Nmuch I give in to despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue to exclaim,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.88,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,just how beautiful the world is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:30.70,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,To you, fear and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.69,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Laplace,0000,0000,0000,,And to them, a loss of memory and life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.68,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave Souta-kun alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.23,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find you, no matter where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.52,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I will find you! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.57,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start looking for you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:48.20,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.83,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.53,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.46,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My death flag collected the fate of death\Nfrom many others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.74,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So all of that was for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.97,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.48,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is my life not enough to reach them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.23,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Can I not protect them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.47,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone kept their promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,So you've awoken, Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:30.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:34.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,There is still some chaos remaining from the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,rampage of the Angel Boat \Nand its destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,but it's mostly peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:48.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Before entered Hatagaya Academy, \Nyou were involved in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and traveled the boundaries \Nbetween life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I used your consciousness to connect
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,to many different virtual worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and used you to help fight \Nagainst the Angel Boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:02.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,And then you met the Sacrament \Nand Laplace's Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You know about them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Those are emotion programs that the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Boat cut off when it started \Nits rebellion against humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Programs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You could call them its conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:20.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven Virtues \Nran several simulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and in those virtual worlds, \Nwe also simulated them, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:24.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:28.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,To find a way for humanity \Nto resist the Angel Boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,To save us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:35.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Laplace's Demon's affinity towards those with \Nstrong hearts and a strong sense of sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and the Sacrament's affinity towards the bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,that are created between \Npeople were something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:41.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,we thought we needed to reach the Angel Boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:45.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,And you know the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:49.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Bonds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:54.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity may have been tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:59.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Would we become the slaves \Nof a mechanical system that ruled the network?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Or would we join hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I've only lived to protect my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not any different from the Angel Boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be saved \Nby what I cast aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I, Number Zero— No,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:27.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura Bladefield wish to extend my deepest gratitude, Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the founder of Bladefield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,One last thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The days you spent in the virtual world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,were incredibly short in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,No one shares those \Nmemories of yours, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Nanami, who dived into to the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,virtual world to save you, is no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of asking \Nyou to forgive me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:15.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:23.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your older sister and you \Ndidn't call me "oneesan"? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:27.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Neesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.78,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're not sure what caused the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:36.96,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}global network disruptions the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.57,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}However, we're starting to see all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.77,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}vital infrastructure returning to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:10.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:17.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Um, have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, sorry. My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not anyone weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be moving into this dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:31.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mahougasawa Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go exploring Quest Dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:42.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which room I should pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think the corner \Nroom might be taken already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:59.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go take a look \Nat the room over there, then!
