Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:21.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hatate-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
